curam.util.client.path.util
Class ClientPaths

java.lang.Object
  curam.util.client.path.util.ClientPaths

public final class ClientPaths
extends java.lang.Object

The main prefix paths used for the data sources accessed by the client infrastructure. The paths defined here correspond to the paths defined in the "paths-config.xml" configuration file. Both definitions must be kept synchronized.
